race.comment: DARK ARTS (1) just ran into one better when resuming at the Sunny Coast and will have come on with that run now under the belt. Gets the services of Maloney in the irons from the inside alley and looks the one they all have to run down. NORTH COURT (5) is a last-start winner who draws well in gate two. Right in the mix in this contest. CANSORT (15) looked handy saluting on debut and will have derived a bunch of benefit from that day at the races. Can go right on with the job now. DETRIMENTAL (3) peaks third-up from the spell and looks one for the exotics players. SMART RECOGNITION (2) next in line with the claim.
